7:
Then when I extinguish you, I will cover the heavens and darken their stars;
\q I will cover the sun with clouds, and the moon will not shine its light.
\q

13:
For I will destroy all the livestock from beside the plentiful waters;
\q the foot of man will no longer stir the waters up, neither will the hooves of cattle stir them.
\q

22:
Assyria is there with all her assembly. Her graves surround her;
\q all of them were killed by the sword.
\q
